{
  "stem": "5644.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not every day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If we got them, if we could get them at that time-- no, not every day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went out to get them, and we couldn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About-- in-- at the-- at the height of the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my book, was from 400,000 to 500,000, approximately. 350,000 to 500,000.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the highest point.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not five guns at a time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One at a time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am not only one buying it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's more people buying it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am not the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not the only one buying it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I did another ways of buying from the organization, or getting from the organization outside, which I got no connection with it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got nothing to-- because you will find in Ringelblum's--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Ringelblum's book, you'll find that we been the most, the most, as from all organizations, having guns, machine guns, and uniforms.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His own-- his own writing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He give you a full-- a full-- it says it was the place which was the most--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We'd been storing them, hiding them in the cellars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then when was the cleaning of the Jews, when they send out the 300,000, and we'd been left 60,000, we opened simply on a ground floor, and first floor, in a wide area, where nobody's coming.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only the Germans can come, and the Polish, to clean our places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did [INAUDIBLE] our, our our stockroom, in our offices, in our bunker,",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our bunker, open completely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the saying was that so ever will come in won't get out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If they are not from the organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "7 9-- two numbers-- Muranowska Street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "7 to 9 Muranowska Street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, because that was two numbers in the street, in this number.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that was a corner place.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
